extendedInfo.description: Rave with your Android phone! This wallpaper turns your Android phone into a strobe light!READ BEFORE DOWNLOADING: This is a live wallpaper, not a standalone app.  Live wallpapers are not run in the same way other apps are.  It will not show up in your app drawer.  You must set it as your wallpaper to run it.  Don't give it a 1-star rating and claim it doesn't work on your phone just because you don't know how to use live wallpapers.WARNING: DO NOT USE IF YOU ARE SUSCEPTIBLE TO SEIZURES OR DISLIKE STROBE LIGHTS!  If you find strobe lights annoying, you will probably also find this live wallpaper annoying.  You've been warned.Check out my other wallpaper: LiveScroller!
